Actions.Prompt:
Enter the Data for Date Conversion

• DateSourceStr -- source date in most any common format

• DateOutputFormat -- Select from list of Unicode formats for output date, very similar to KM ISU date/time format codes.  Click "Help" button (⌘H) for details and examples.

• OtherDateFormat -- Manual override of output date format. 

.
